result.execSummary:
The defendant Justin John Tranby 642524 was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Justin John Tranby 642524 is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Justin John Tranby 642524 was found guilty of Possess w/ Intent-Amphetamine(>10-50g) [Modifiers: Penalties for Felonies-Class "D" Felony], a class D felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(1m)(e)3.

In the event that the defendant is revoked or discharged from either probation or extended supervision with outstanding financial obligations, the supervising agent shall notify the court 10 days prior to the revocation or discharge. All available enforcement actions will be used to collect all debt.

110 days credit against sentence

- Random and regular testing.
